      <title>软银债券承销费十年来首次下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/softbank-s-bond-underwriting-fee-drops-for-first-time-in-decade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[软银集团十年来首次下调日元零售债券的承销费，凸显出市场对其信用质量正在改善的看法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/softbank-s-bond-underwriting-fee-drops-for-first-time-in-decade</guid>
