    <item>
      <title>印度股市因选举失利而反弹，速度为十年来最快</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/india-s-stock-rebound-from-election-upset-is-fastest-in-a-decade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度股市以近代历史上最快的速度摆脱了选举冲击，国内投资者利用上周近 4000 亿美元的抛售作为逢低买入的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/india-s-stock-rebound-from-election-upset-is-fastest-in-a-decade</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 06:44:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>维勒鲁瓦表示，下一届法国政府需要明确的财政战略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/next-french-government-needs-a-clear-fiscal-strategy-villeroy-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国央行行长弗朗索瓦·维勒鲁瓦德加洛表示，法国下一届政府必须迅速明确其经济政策，因为提前选举导致投资者恐慌，抛售法国债券并推高借贷成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/next-french-government-needs-a-clear-fiscal-strategy-villeroy-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 06:42:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿布扎比今年首支 IPO 上市首日下跌 10%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/abu-dhabi-s-first-ipo-of-the-year-falls-10-in-trading-debut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Alef Education 在阿布扎比首次上市时融资 18.9 亿迪拉姆（5.15 亿美元），但随后股价下跌，这在中东实属罕见。在中东，首次公开募股 (IPO) 通常在早盘交易中就能带来近乎保证的回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/abu-dhabi-s-first-ipo-of-the-year-falls-10-in-trading-debut</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 06:28:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
